- `scripts/migrate_artifacts.py` ‚Äî idempotent cleanup of legacy paths.
- `data_simulation/kafka_stream.py` ‚Äî Kafka iterator adapter for the pipeline.
- `run_kafka_producer.py` / `run_streaming_kafka.py` ‚Äî Kafka produce/consume entry points.

